data.description: Quant and recently updated this little cabin sits on a shady lot just outside of Catifish Bay on Lake Texoma.  The gated entry into the property is automatic and provides additional security for an "already quite" neighborhood.  The back yard is completely enclosed by a wooden privacy fence.  Combined with the covered patio this makes an exceptional area for family or entertaining guests.  There is room for RV parking on the side of the house, and a storm shelter in the front yard for when the sky threatens to get nasty.  This property sells partially furnished, and is less than a 10-minute drive from Catfish Bay Marina, Boat Ramps, Gas Docks, Campsites, Chickasaw Point Golf Course, and the New Westbay Casino and Resort.
